features: [Wide-Open Design] - With its wide zip opening, this makeup bag allows for easy retrieval of your daily cosmetics, skincare products, and toiletry accessories. The multi-pocket design ensures that your cosmetics stay neatly organized.

[Quilted Makeup Bag] - This compact makeup bag features exquisite quilting. It is crafted from water-resistant peach-skin fabric, providing a soft and luxurious feel. The stitching and elegant zipper not only demonstrate excellent craftsmanship but also add a touch of sophistication and style.

[Practical Makeup Organizer Bag] - Designed for women, this makeup bag measures 6.63 x 5.1 x 3 inches, offering ample space to organize full-sized cosmetics, travel toiletries, beauty tools, and body care items. The main compartment includes two mesh pockets for easy access to small items.

[Multi-functional] - This makeup travel bag serves not only as a cosmetic bag but also as a travel toiletry bag for women. It is suitable for carrying various travel essentials, bringing great convenience to your daily beauty routine.

[Wonderful Gift] - This cosmetic travel bag makes an ideal gift for birthdays, Valentine's Day, Christmas, and for those who frequently travel. Our toiletry travel bag is designed for both journeys and everyday use. It is lightweight yet sturdy, offering enough space to hold all your toiletries and personal travel items.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and very functional bag!
reviews.reviewText: This seemingly small bag packs a big punch. I utilize it for toiletries while traveling, and it can hold a lot of products. It's soft, but holds its shape well, even after being packed in my backpack and suitcases. They look elegant, but you can totally use them without fear of ruining them. They wipe off and clean-up easily too. I love it so much, I ordered some as gifts.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful and well made!
reviews.reviewText: The size is perfect, it holds so much and looks very classy. I love the fabric inside and outside and the color is a tasteful shade of feminine pink, I love it!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect little bag
reviews.reviewText: I don't use a lot of makeup, so it's nice to have something small that still allows me to organize the makeup I do have. It will also be perfect for travel. It's very cute, too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I love this little bag. It is the perfect size for traveling. It fits all of my essentials just right. (2 brushes, foundation, highlighter, blush, eyeliner, mascara, and brow powder.) I don't wear much so it works great for me. If you need more space, they have a bigger size too! The color is beautiful and it is very well made.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice makeup bag, but it’s really small!!
reviews.reviewText: I should’ve paid more attention to the measurements of this bag! It’s tiny! I can fit a few basic makeup supplies in it, but not everything I use (moisturizer, primer, concealer, liquid makeup, blush, eyeliner, highlighter, setting powder, setting spray, plus various brushes). I’m not exactly sure what I’ll use it for just yet, but it’s a nice bag in a great color for a good price, so I’m keeping it. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST MAKEUP BAG
reviews.reviewText: This bag truly fits all my makeup. I have a lot and it has many different sides and 2 zippers to add extra things as well as compartments inside the pouch for holding brushes too. It’s not too big to be bulky and not too small. it fits all the things needed and super cute tassel as a zipper to add more to the bag. Other than the fact that I love the color, the size and shape is very convenient!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly what I needed
reviews.reviewText: This was my first purchase of a bagsmart product. I ordered to replace a purse/bag organizer. This one is SO much better! It feels very well made. I love the exterior pocket and the interior organization. I washed it in the machine on delicate and it air-dried perfectly. It fits everything I need so when I change bags I just have to grab this and put it in the next bag and I'm ready to go. I love it so much that I've since ordered travel pouches, compression packing cubes also from bagsmart and they have been just as amazing. Debating ordering a duffle next because I'm out of control lol

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 5, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bedside bag.
reviews.reviewText: Great bag to keep at my bedside during a total knee replacement. Love the side pocket for my strong meds!
